                    <h2 data-uuid="a28b5884b07147bda1be892de6044e24">Anti-Abolitionist Rally</h2>
                    <p class="source" data-uuid="5b7cb5f9d5f34dc5aebc1f2f51122c89">Members of an anti-abolitionist group used this flyer to call people together in order to disrupt a meeting of abolitionists in 1837.</p>
